無回音，剩下嘅只有無了期嘅等待。<br />\n<br />\n聯合國曾建議單獨囚禁應以 15 日為上限，但點解香港從來無落實有關建議呢？點解連單獨囚禁嘅時間上限都無呢？點解懲教會唔提供一套完善嘅上訴機制，及定期覆查機制比單獨囚禁者呢？小編對呢一切有好多困惑。<br />\n<br />\n但始終最令我困惑嘅係，點解陳同佳呢啲殺人犯可以住喺豪宅，但區區參加過初選嘅人，就要被單獨關押喺牢房入面呢？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9E%97%E5%8D%93%E5%BB%B7%E5%96%AE%E7%8D%A8%E5%9B%9A%E7%A6%81%E7%AC%AC-17-%E6%97%A5-%E8%AA%BF%E5%80%89%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E7%84%A1%E5%9B%9E%E9%9F%B3/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E5%258D%2593%25E5%25BB%25B7%25E5%2596%25AE%25E7%258D%25A8%25E5%259B%259A%25E7%25A6%2581%25E7%25AC%25AC-17-%25E6%2597%25A5-%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E5%2580%2589%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%259B%259E%25E9%259F%25B3%2F&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2Rx3ZeYPbPBc9Z3MXbd07rU%3D&h=eea4a1b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E5%258D%2593%25E5%25BB%25B7%25E5%2596%25AE%25E7%258D%25A8%25E5%259B%259A%25E7%25A6%2581%25E7%25AC%25AC-17-%25E6%2597%25A5-%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E5%2580%2589%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%259B%259E%25E9%259F%25B3%2F&h=8f9c0003\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9E%97%E5%8D%93%E5%BB%B7%E5%96%AE%E7%8D%A8%E5%9B%9A%E7%A6%81%E7%AC%AC-17-%E6%97%A5-%E8%AA%BF%E5%80%89%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E7%84%A1%E5%9B%9E%E9%9F%B3/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T12:53:51.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">Fuck you CCP</span></span>"},{"pid":"9d6c745d094555e99ea484b52c372e45aa56d784","tid":2451849,"uid":194120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T13:00:28.000Z","msg":"中國就係要折磨到你痴線"},{"pid":"2673e7fb4b8fc05f92a42d6379710df91b81438d","tid":2451849,"uid":204539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T13:02:06.000Z","msg":"仲要依家只係還押<br />\n都未撚判佢有罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.